# ChatInterface Component Description

This file (`src/components/ChatInterface.tsx`) defines the `ChatInterface` React component. This component provides a chat-like interface for interacting with different AI agents within the Nellia Prospector dashboard.

Key features:
- Allows users to select an agent to chat with via tabs.
- Displays message history for each agent.
- Provides an input field to send messages to the selected agent.
- Includes a simulated agent response mechanism.
- Uses the `useTranslation` hook for internationalization.
- Visually indicates agent status.

